obj_root_law:
  slug the-delhi-municipal-corporation-act-1957
  handle (1410)
  collectionHandle 123456789/1362
  title `The Delhi Municipal Corporation Act, 1957`
  actNumber (66)
  enactmentDate 1957-12-28
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/1410`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  actYear (1957)
  ministry `Ministry of Home Affairs`
  department `Department of States`
  longTitle `An Act to consolidate and amend the law relating to the Municipal Government of Delhi.`
  enforcementDate 02-01-1958
  notification `2nd January, 1958, vide notification No. F. 20/3/58/SR (R), dated 31st December, 1957, in respect of S. 2, Chap. II, ss. 54, 55, 56, 57, 58, 59, 89 and 97, Chap. XXIII, ss. 485, 487, 488, 491, 500, 509, 513 and 515, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part IV. 15th February, 1958, vide notification No. F. 20/3/58/SR (R), dated 11th February, 1958, in respect of S. 510, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part IV. 7th April, 1958, vide notification No. F. 20/3/58/SR (R), dated 5th April, 1958, in respect of All the provisions of the Act (other than those which have already been brought into force), see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part IV.`
