  line
  line `11. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 6, for sub-sections (5) and (6) (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
  line
  line `12. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 5, for sub-sections (5) and (6) (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
  line
  line `13. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011,s. 2, for "the area of the corporation" (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
  line
  line `14. Subs. by Act 67 of 1993, s. 3, for sub-section (7) (w.e.f 1-10-1993).`
