  line
  line `2. Subs. by s. 2, ibid., for "the Corporation" (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
  line
  line `3. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 2, for "every Corporation" (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
  line
  line `4. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for "Central Government" (w.e.f.13-1-2012).`
  line
  line `5. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 2, for "Government" (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
