obj_root_law_sections_82_content:
  string
  line `^1[^2[The Corporation]] may make regulations for the transaction of`
  line `business at its meeting:`
  line
  line `Provided that the time, place and procedure for the first meeting after the constitution of ^3[^4[the`
  line `Corporation]] under section 3 shall be determined by the Administrator.`
obj_root_law_sections_82_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for “The Corporation” (w.e.f. 13-1-2012)`
  line .
  line `2. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 2, for “A Corporation” (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
  line
  line `3. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2 “the Corporation” (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
  line
  line `4. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 2, for “a Corporation” (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
obj_root_law_sections_83:
  sectionId (27209)
  sectionNo (83)
  orderNo 102
  title `Presiding officers at meetings of the Standing and other committees.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_83_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_83_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=27209&sectionno=83&orderno=102&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_83_content:
  string
  line `(1) The Chairman or in`
  line `his absence the Deputy Chairman shall preside at every meeting of the Standing Committee, the ^1[Wards`
  line `Committee] or any other committee of the Corporation.`
  line
  line `(2) In the absence of the Chairman and the Deputy Chairman from any meeting the members of any`
  line `such committee shall choose one ^2[from amongst the councillors] to preside over the meeting.`
obj_root_law_sections_83_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Subs. by Act 67 of 1993, s. 62, for certain words (w.e.f. 1-10-1993).`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by s. 62, ibid., for of their numbers (w.e.f. 1-10-1993)`
