obj_root_law_sections_84_content:
  string
  line `^1[^2[The Corporation]] may`
  line `make regulations for the procedure and the conduct of business at meetings, of the Standing Committee`
  line `and all other committees except adhoc committees which shall regulate their own procedure.`
