obj_root_law_sections_163_content:
  string
  line `If any building is wholly or partly demolished or destroyed or`
  line `otherwise deprived of value, the Commissioner may, on the application in writing of the owner or`
  line `occupier, remit or refund such portion of any tax assessed on the rateable annual value thereof as he`
  line `thinks fit.`
