  sectionNo (184)
  orderNo 230
  title Omitted..
  content `184. [Proceeds of entertainment tax.] Omitted by Delhi Act No. 11 of 2002, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-1996).`
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_184_footnotes
