obj_root_law_sections_507:
  sectionId (31427)
  sectionNo (507)
  orderNo 568
  title `Special provisions as to rural areas.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_507_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_507_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=31427&sectionno=507&orderno=568&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_507_content:
  string
  line `Notwithstanding anything contained in the foregoing`
  line `provisions of this Act,---`
  line
  line `(a) ^1[^2[the Corporation]] with the previous approval of the ^3`
  line `*** Government, may, by notification in`
  line `the Official Gazette, declare that any portion of the rural areas shall cease to be included therein and`
  line `upon the issue of such notification that portion shall be included in and form part of the urban areas;`
  line
  line `(b) ^1[^2[the Corporation]] with the previous approval of the ^3`
  line `*** Government may, by notification in`
  line `the Official Gazette,--`
  line
  line `(i) exempt the rural areas or any portion thereof from such of the provisions of this Act as it`
  line `deems fit,`
  line
  line `(ii) levy taxes, rates, fees and other charges in the rural areas or any portion thereof at rates`
  line `lower than those at which such taxes, rates, fees and other charges are levied in the urban areas or`
  line `exempt such areas or portion from any such tax, rate, fee or other charge;`
  line
  line `(c) ^1[^2[the Corporation]] shall pay a Gaon Sabha---`
  line
  line `(i) an amount equal to the proceeds of the tax on profession, trades, callings and`
  line `employments, as and when that tax is levied in the Gaon Sabha area, and`
  line
  line `(ii) an amount equal to such portion of the proceeds of the property taxes on lands and`
  line `buildings in that area as may from time to time to be determined by ^1[^2[the Corporation]],`
  line
  line `after deducting the cost of collection from such proceeds.`
  line
  line `Explanation.In this section the expressions Gaon Sabha and Gaon Sabha area have the same`
  line `meanings as in the Delhi Panchayat Raj Act, 1954 (Delhi Act 3 of 1955).`
obj_root_law_sections_507_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for “the Corporation” (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 2, for “a Corporation” (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
  line
  line `3. The word Central omitted by s. 130, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-10-1993).`
obj_root_law_sections_508:
  sectionId (31428)
  sectionNo (508)
  orderNo 569
  title `Special provisions as to Red Fort area.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_508_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_508_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=31428&sectionno=508&orderno=569&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_508_content:
  string
  line `(1) In administering the provisions of this Act within`
  line `the Red Fort area ^1[^2[the Corporation]] shall comply with the military rules and regulations for the time being`
  line `in force within that area.`
  line
  line `(2) In this section the expression Red Fort area means the Red Fort and such areas continuous`
  line `thereto as may be declared by the ^3[Government] by notification in the Gazette of India to be`
  line `included within the Red Fort area.`
obj_root_law_sections_508_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for "the Corporation"(w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 2, for "a Corporation" (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
  line
  line `3. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for "Central Government" (w.e.f. 13-1-2012)`
obj_root_law_sections_508_a:
  sectionId (31429)
  sectionNo 508A
  orderNo 570
  title `Corporation to undertake work on agency basis.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_508_a_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_508_a_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=31429&sectionno=508A&orderno=570&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_508_a_content:
  string
  line ^1
  line `[508A. Corporation to undertake work on agency basis.---Notwithstanding anything contained in`
  line `any other provision of this Act, ^2[^3[the Corporation]] may on such terms and conditions as may be determined by agreement between ^2[^3[the Corporation]] and any authority, body or person, carry out any work which is not`
  line `connected with its functions on agency basis.]`
obj_root_law_sections_508_a_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Ins. by Act 67 of 1993, s. 131 (w.e.f. 1-10-1993).`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for the Corporation (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
  line
  line `3. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 2, for a Corporation (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
