  line
obj_root_law_sections_510:
  sectionId (31431)
  sectionNo (510)
  orderNo 572
  title `Provisions relating to existing local authorities in Delhi till the establishment of the Corporation.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_510_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_510_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=31431&sectionno=510&orderno=572&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_510_content:
  string
  line `(1) Notwithstanding anything contained in the Punjab Municipal Act, 1911 (Punjab`
  line `Act 3 of 1911) or as the case may be, the Punjab District Boards Act, 1883, (20 of 1883) as in force in`
  line `Delhi, as from the commencement of this Act,--`
  line
  line `(a) the persons who immediately before such commencement are members of any of the local`
  line `authorities specified in items 1 to 10 of the Second Schedule shall cease to be such members;`
  line
  line `(b) all the powers, duties and functions which may, under any of the aforesaid Acts or any other`
  line `law, be exercised and performed by any such local authority, or by its President or Chairman, or by`
  line `any Committee thereof shall, until the establishment of ^1[^2[the Corporation]], be exercised and performed`
  line `by a person (whether an officer of Government or not) to be appointed by the Central Government`
  line `with such designation as it may specify:`
  line
  line `Provided that the same person may be appointed in respect of all the aforesaid local authorities.`
  line
  line `(2) Nothing in sub-section (1) shall be construed as effecting or implying in any way the dissolution`
  line `of the aforesaid local authorities as bodies corporate.`
obj_root_law_sections_510_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for “the Corporation” (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 2, for “a Corporation” (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
obj_root_law_sections_511:
  sectionId (31432)
  sectionNo (511)
  orderNo 573
  title `Provisions as to employees of bodies and local authorities whose functions are taken over by the Corporation.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_511_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_511_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=31432&sectionno=511&orderno=573&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_511_content:
  string
  line `511. Provisions as to employees of bodies and local authorities whose functions are taken over by ^1[^2[the Corporation]].---(1) Every officer and other employee of each of the bodies and local authorities`
  line `specified in the Second Schedule shall, on and from the establishment of the Corporation, be transferred`
  line `to and become an officer or other employee of ^1[^2[the Corporation]] with such designation as the`
  line `Commissioner may determine and shall hold office by the same tenure, at the same remuneration and on`
  line `the same terms and conditions of service as he would have held the same if ^1[^2[the Corporation]] had not been`
  line `established, and shall continue to do so unless and until such tenure, remuneration and terms and`
  line `conditions are duly altered by ^1[^2[the Corporation]]:`
  line
  line `Provided that the tenure, remuneration and terms and conditions of service of any such officer or`
  line `other employee shall not be altered to his disadvantage without the previous sanction of the ^3[Government]:`
  line
  line `Provided further that any service rendered by any such officer or other employee before the`
  line `establishment of ^1[^2[the Corporation]] shall be deemed to be service rendered under ^1[^2[the Corporation]].`
  line
  line `(2) The Commissioner may employ any officer or other employee transferred to ^1[^2[the Corporation]]`
  line `under sub-section (1) in the discharge of such functions under this Act as the Commissioner may think`
  line `proper and every such officer or other employee shall discharge those functions accordingly.`
obj_root_law_sections_511_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for "the Corporation" (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 2, for "a Corporation" (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
  line
  line `3. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for “Central Government” (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
obj_root_law_sections_511_a:
  sectionId (31433)
  sectionNo 511A
  orderNo 574
  title `Temporary provision with respect to electricity, water, sewage, etc.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_511_a_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_511_a_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=31433&sectionno=511A&orderno=574&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_511_a_content:
  string
  line `^1[511A. Temporary provision with respect to electricity, water, sewage, etc.Notwithstanding`
  line `the commencement of the Delhi Municipal Corporation (Amendment) Act, 1993, all the provisions`
  line `existing in the principal Act before such commencement relating to`
  line
  line `(a) water supply, drainage and sewage disposal;`
  line
  line `(b) electric supply; and`
  line
  line `(c) prevention and extinguishing of fire,`
  line
  line `and matters connected therewith or incidental thereto shall be deemed to continue in operation till such`
  line `date as the ^2[Government] may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify and different dates`
  line `may be specified by the Central Government for any of the aforementioned different matters.]`
obj_root_law_sections_511_a_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Ins. by Act 67 of 1993, s. 133 (w.e.f. 1-10-1993).`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for “Central Government” (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
obj_root_law_sections_511_b:
  sectionId (31434)
  sectionNo 511B
  orderNo 575
  title `Special provision as to transferred functions.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_511_b_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_511_b_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=31434&sectionno=511B&orderno=575&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_511_b_content:
  string
  line `^1[511B. Special provision as to transferred functions.-- (1) In this section, transferred functions`
  line `means such functions of ^2[^3[the Corporation]] which immediately before the commencement of the Delhi`
  line `Municipal Corporation (Amendment) Act,1993 were the functions of ^2[^3[the Corporation]] but as from such`
  line `commencement become the functions of any other authority or functionary hereinafter called the new`
  line authority.
  line
  line `(2) On and from such commencement,--`
  line
  line `(a) all lands and buildings (together with all interests of whatsoever nature and kind therein)`
  line `vested in ^2[^3[the Corporation]] immediately before such commencement and used for the purposes of`
  line `transferred functions shall pass to and vest in the new authority concerned;`
  line
  line `(b) all stores, articles and other movable properties belonging to ^2[^3[the Corporation]] immediately`
  line `before such commencement and utilised for or in connection with the transferred functions shall`
  line `pass to and vest in the new authority concerned;`
  line
  line `(c) all appointment, notifications, orders, schemes, rules, forms, notices or bye-laws made or`
  line `issued or any licence or permissions granted by ^2[^3[the Corporation]] immediately before such`
  line `commencement in connection with the transferred functions shall continue in force and be deemed`
  line `to have been made, issued or granted by the new authority concerned unless and until they are`
  line `superseded by any appointment, notification, order, scheme, rule, form, notice or bye-law made or`
  line `issued or any licence or permission granted by the new authority concerned;`
  line
  line `(d) all debts, obligations and liabilities incurred, all contracts entered into and all matters and`
  line `things engaged to be done by, with or for, ^2[^3[the Corporation]] immediately before such commencement`
  line `for or in connection with the transferred functions shall be deemed to have been incurred, entered`
  line `into, engaged to be done by, with or for, the new authority concerned;`
  line
  line `(e) all assessments, valuations, measurements or divisions made by ^2[^3[the Corporation]] immediately`
  line `before such commencement in or in connection with the transferred functions shall continue in`
  line `force and be deemed to have been made by the new authority concerned unless and until they are`
  line `superseded by any assessment, valuation, measurement or division made by that authority;`
  line
  line `(f) all rates, taxes, fees, rents and other sums of money due to ^2[^3[the Corporation]] in relation to the`
  line `transferred functions immediately before such commencement shall be deemed to be due to the`
  line `new authority concerned;`
  line
  line `(g) all rates, fees, rents and other charges leviable in, or in relation to, the transferred functions`
  line `shall, unless and until they are varied by the new authority concerned continue to be levied at the`
  line `same rate at which they were being levied by ^2[^3[the Corporation]] immediately before such`
  line commencement;
  line
  line `(h) all suits, prosecutions and other legal proceedings instituted or which might have been`
  line `instituted by or against ^2[^3[the Corporation]] immediately before such commencement for any matter in`
  line `relation to the transferred functions may be continued or instituted by or against the new authority`
  line concerned;
  line
  line `(i) every officer and other employee serving under ^2[^3[the Corporation]] immediately before such`
  line `commencement in connection with the transferred functions shall be transferred to and become an`
  line `officer or other employee of the new authority concerned with such designation as such authority may`
  line `determine and hold office by the same tenure and at the same remuneration and on the same terms`
  line `and conditions of service as he would have held the same is the new authority concerned had not been`
  line `established and shall continue to do so unless and until such tenure, remuneration and terms and`
  line `conditions are duly altered by that authority:`
  line
  line `Provided that the tenure, remuneration and terms and conditions of service of any such officer or`
  line `other employee shall not be altered to his disadvantage without the previous sanction of the Central`
  line `Government:`
  line `Provided further that any service rendered by any such officer or other employee before such`
  line `commencement shall be deemed to be service rendered under the new authority concerned:`
  line
  line `Provided also that the new authority concerned may employ any such officer or other employee in the`
  line `discharge of such functions as it may think proper and every such officer or other employee shall`
  line `discharge those functions accordingly.`
  line
  line `(3) As soon as may be after the commencement of the Delhi Municipal Corporation (Amendment)`
  line `Act, 1993, the ^4[Central Government] shall decide,--`
  line
  line `(a) which stores, articles and other movable properties referred to in clause (b) of sub-section (2)`
  line `have been utilised by ^2[^3[the Corporation]] for or in connection with the transferred functions;`
  line
  line `(b) which debts, obligations, liabilities, contracts, matters and things referred to in clause (d) of`
  line `the said sub-section have been incurred, entered into or engaged to be done by, with or for ^2[^3[the Corporation]] for or in connection with the transferred functions;`
  line
  line `(c) which officers and other employees referred to in clause (i) of that sub-section served under`
  line `^2[^3[the Corporation]] in connection with the transferred functions.`
  line
  line `(4) In case of any dispute in relation to any of the matters referred to in the various clauses of`
  line `sub-section (2) other than clauses (b), (d) and (i), the dispute may be referred to the Central Government`
  line `by the Corporation or the new authority concerned and the decision of that Government shall be final.]`
obj_root_law_sections_511_b_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Ins. by Act 67 of 1993, s. 133 (w.e.f. 1-10-1993).`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for “the Corporation” (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
  line
  line `3. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 2, for “a Corporation” (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
  line
  line `4. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for “Central Government” (w.e.f. 13-1-2012)`
obj_root_law_sections_512:
  sectionId (31435)
  sectionNo (512)
  orderNo 576
  title `Special provisions as to the area transferred from New Delhi to Delhi`
  content obj_root_law_sections_512_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_512_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=31435&sectionno=512&orderno=576&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_512_content:
  string
  line `(1) In this section`
  line `transferred area means that area of Delhi which immediately before the commencement of this Act is`
  line `included within the local limits of the New Delhi Municipal Committee but as from such commencement`
  line `is included in and forms part of Delhi by virtue of the provisions of this Act.`
  line
  line `(2) As from the establishment of ^1[^2[the Corporation]],---`
  line
  line `(a) all lands and buildings (together with all interests of whatsoever nature and kind therein)`
  line `situated in the transferred area and vested in the New Delhi Municipal Committee immediately before`
  line `such establishment shall pass to and vest in ^1[^2[the Corporation]];`
  line
  line `(b) all stores, articles and other movable properties belonging to the New Delhi Municipal`
  line `Committee immediately before such establishment and utilised for or in connection with the`
  line `transferred area shall pass to and vest in ^1[^2[the Corporation]];`
  line
  line `(c) all appointments, notifications, orders, schemes, rules, forms, notices or bye-laws made or`
  line `issued or any licence or permission granted by the New Delhi Municipal Committee immediately`
  line `before such establishment in or in connection with the transferred area shall, in so far as they are not`
  line `inconsistent with the provisions of this Act continue in force and be deemed to have been made,`
  line `issued or granted under the provisions of this Act unless and until they are superseded by any`
  line `appointment, notification, order, scheme, rule, form, notice or bye-law made or issued or any licence`
  line `or permission granted under the said provisions;`
  line
  line `(d) all debts, obligations and liabilities incurred, all contracts entered into and all matters and`
  line `things engaged to be done by, with or for the New Delhi Municipal Committee immediately before`
  line `such establishment for or in connection with the transferred area shall be deemed to have been`
  line `incurred, entered into, engaged to be done by, with or for ^1[^2[the Corporation]] or the municipal authority`
  line concerned;
  line
  line `(e) all assessments, valuations, measurements or divisions made by the New Delhi Municipal`
  line `Committee immediately before such establishment in or in connection with the transferred area shall`
  line `in so far as they are not inconsistent with the provisions of this Act, continue in force and be deemed`
  line `to have been made under the provisions of this Act unless and until they are superseded by any assessment, valuation, measurement or division made by ^1[^2[the Corporation]] or the municipal authority`
  line `concerned under the said provisions;`
  line
  line `(f) all rates, taxes, fees, rents and other sums of money due to the New Delhi Municipal`
  line `Committee in, or in relation to, the transferred area immediately before such establishment shall be`
  line `deemed to be due to the Corporation;`
  line
  line `(g) all rates, taxes, fees, rents and other charges leviable in, or in relation to, the transferred area`
  line `shall unless and until they are varied by ^1[^2[the Corporation]], continue to be levied at the same rate at`
  line `which they were being levied by the New Delhi Municipal Committee immediately before such`
  line establishment;
  line
  line `(h) all suits, prosecutions and other legal proceedings instituted or which might have been`
  line `instituted by or against the New Delhi Municipal Committee immediately before such establishment`
  line `for any matter in relation to the transferred area may be continued or instituted by or against ^1[^2[the`
  line Corporation]];
  line
  line `(i) every officer and other employee serving under the New Delhi Municipal Committee`
  line `immediately before such establishment in connection with the transferred area shall be transferred to`
  line `and become an officer or other employee of ^1[^2[the Corporation]] with such designation as the`
  line `Commissioner may determine and hold office by the same tenure and at the same remuneration and`
  line `on the same terms and conditions of service as he would have held the same if ^1[^2[the Corporation]] had`
  line `not been established and shall continue to do so unless and until such tenure, remuneration and terms`
  line `and conditions are duly altered by ^1[^2[the Corporation]] :`
  line
  line `Provided that the tenure, remuneration and terms and conditions of service of any such officer or`
  line `other employee shall not be altered to his disadvantage without the previous sanction of the Central`
  line `Government:`
  line
  line `Provided further that any service rendered by any such officer or other employee before the`
  line `establishment of ^1[^2[the Corporation]] shall be deemed to be service rendered under ^1[^2[the Corporation]]:`
  line
  line `Provided also that the Commissioner may employ any such officer or other employee in the discharge`
  line `of such functions under this Act as the Commissioner may think proper and every such officer or other`
  line `employee shall discharge those functions accordingly.`
  line
  line `(3) As soon as may be after the commencement of this Act, the ^3[Government] shall decide---`
  line
  line `(a) which stores, articles and other movable properties referred to in clause (b) of sub-section (2)`
  line `have been utilised by the New Delhi Municipal Committee for or in connection with the transferred`
  line area;
  line
  line `(b) which debts, obligations, liabilities, contracts, matters and things referred to in clause (d) of`
  line `the said sub-section have been incurred, entered into or engaged to be done by, with or for the New`
  line `Delhi Municipal Committee for or in connection with the transferred area;`
  line
  line `(c) which officers and other employees referred to in clause (i) of that sub-section served under`
  line `the said committee in connection with the transferred area.`
  line
  line `(4) In case of any dispute in relation to any of the matters referred to in the various clauses of`
  line `sub-section (2) other than clauses (b), (d) and (i), the dispute may be referred to the Central Government`
  line `by ^1[^2[the Corporation]] or the New Delhi Municipal Committee and the decision of that Government shall be`
  line final
obj_root_law_sections_512_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for “the Corporation” (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 2, for “a Corporation” (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
  line
  line `3. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for “Central Government” (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
obj_root_law_sections_513:
  sectionId (31436)
  sectionNo (513)
  orderNo 577
  title `Expenditure in connection with the Municipal Affairs from the commencement of this Act to the adoption of the budget by a Corporation.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_513_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_513_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=31436&sectionno=513&orderno=577&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_513_content:
  string
  line `(1) Any expenditure incurred during the period`
  line `between the commencement of this Act and the establishment of ^1[^2[the Corporation]] under any of the`
  line `provisions of this Act shall be borne by the Central Government and the amount of the expenditure so`
  line `incurred shall on such establishment be recoverable by that Government out of the Municipal Fund.`
  line
  line `(2) If in respect of the period between the establishment of ^1[^2[the Corporation]] and the adoption of the`
  line `first budget by ^1[^2[the Corporation]] further expenditure from the Municipal Fund becomes necessary over and above the expenditure thereto for authorised for that year by the sanctioned budget estimates of the`
  line `various bodies and local authorities specified in the Second Schedule, ^1[^2[the Corporation]] shall adopt a`
  line `supplementary statement showing the estimated amount of that expenditure.`
  line
  line `(3) Every item of expenditure shown in the supplementary statement as adopted by ^1[^2[the Corporation]]`
  line `shall be deemed to be expenditure covered by a current budget-grant within the meaning of section102.`
  line
  line `(4) The supplementary statement shall be prepared, presented and adopted in such manner and shall`
  line `provide for such matters as may be determined by ^1[^2[the Corporation]] .`
obj_root_law_sections_513_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for “the Corporation” (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).br`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 2, for “a Corporation” (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
obj_root_law_sections_514:
  sectionId (31437)
  sectionNo (514)
  orderNo 578
  title `Limits of New Delhi Municipality.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_514_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_514_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=31437&sectionno=514&orderno=578&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_514_content:
  string
  line `Notwithstanding anything contained in the Punjab`
  line `Municipal Act, 1911, (Punjab Act 3 of 1911) as applicable to New Delhi Municipality or in any`
  line `notification issued thereunder, the limits of that Municipality shall be as described in the First Schedule.`
obj_root_law_sections_514_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_514_a:
  sectionId (31438)
  sectionNo 514A
  orderNo 579
  title `Appointment of Special Officer`
  content obj_root_law_sections_514_a_content
  footnotes `1. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 13, for section 514A (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=31438&sectionno=514A&orderno=579&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_514_a_content:
  string
  line ^1
  line `[514A.Appointment of Special Officer.—Notwithstanding anything contained in this Act, the`
  line `Central Government may, if necessary, appoint a person to be called the Special Officer, to exercise the`
  line `power and discharge the functions of the Corporation until the date on which the first meeting of the`
  line `Corporation is held after the commencement of the Delhi Municipal Corporation (Amendment) Act, 2022.]`
obj_root_law_sections_514_aa:
  sectionId (67093)
  sectionNo 514AA
  orderNo 580
  title `Transitional provisions`
  content obj_root_law_sections_514_aa_content
  footnotes `1. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 13, for section 514A (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=67093&sectionno=514AA&orderno=580&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_514_aa_content:
  string
  line `^1[514AA. Transitional provisions.---On and from the commencement of the Delhi Municipal`
  line `Corporation (Amendment) Act, 2022, ---`
  line
  line `(a) the North Delhi Municipal Corporation, the South Delhi Municipal Corporation and the East`
  line `Delhi Municipal Corporation (hereafter referred to as the erstwhile Corporations) shall be subsumed`
  line `with, and become part of the Municipal Corporation of Delhi;`
  line
  line `(b) any reference to the erstwhile Corporations in any contract or other instrument shall be deemed`
  line `as a reference to the Municipal Corporation of Delhi;`
  line
  line `(c) all properties, movable and immovable, of or belonging to the erstwhile Corporations shall vest`
  line `in the Municipal Corporation of Delhi;`
  line
  line `(d) all the rights and liabilities of the erstwhile Corporations shall be transferred to, and be the rights`
  line `and liabilities of, the Municipal Corporation of Delhi;`
  line
  line `(e) any pending proceedings, including any disciplinary, arbitration, appeal or other legal`
  line `proceedings, of whatever nature, by or against the erstwhile Corporations shall be continued or enforced`
  line `by or against the Municipal Corporation of Delhi;`
  line
  line `(f) any rules, regulations and bye-laws made prior to such commencement, shall, in so far as they`
  line `are consistent with the provisions of the Act, continue to be applicable till new rules, regulations and`
  line `bye-laws are made.]`
obj_root_law_sections_514_b:
  sectionId (67094)
  sectionNo 514B
  orderNo 581
  title `Overriding effect of the provisions of the Delhi Development Act, 1957.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_514_b_content
  footnotes `1. Ins. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 21 (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=67094&sectionno=514B&orderno=581&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_514_b_content:
  string
  line `^1[514-B. Overriding effect of the provisions of the Delhi Development Act, 1957.—Notwithstanding`
  line `anything contained in this Act, in case of any repugnancy between the provisions of this Act and the`
  line `provisions of the Delhi Development Act, 1957, the provisions of the Delhi Development Act, 1957 shall`
  line `prevail over the provisions of this Act.]`
obj_root_law_sections_515:
  sectionId (31439)
  sectionNo (515)
  orderNo 582
  title `Power to remove difficulties.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_515_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_515_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=31439&sectionno=515&orderno=582&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_515_content:
  string
  line `If any difficulty arises in relation to the transition from the`
  line `provisions of any of the enactments referred to in section 516, or in giving effect to the provisions of this`
  line `Act, the ^1[Government] may, by order as occasion requires, do anything which appears to it to be`
  line `necessary for the purpose of removing the difficulty:`
  line
  line `Provided that no such order shall be made after the expiration of two years from the establishment of`
  line `^2[^3[the corporation]].`
obj_root_law_sections_515_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for “the Corporation” (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 2, for “a Corporation” (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
obj_root_law_sections_516:
  sectionId (31440)
  sectionNo (516)
  orderNo 583
  title `Repeal, etc., and savings.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_516_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_516_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857&sectionId=31440&sectionno=516&orderno=583&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00028_195766_1517807321857
obj_root_law_sections_516_content:
  string
  line `(1) As from the date of the establishment of ^1[^2[the Corporation]],--`
  line
  line `(a) the Delhi Joint Water Sewage Board Act,1926, (23 of 1926) and the Delhi Road Transport`
  line `Authority Act, 1950, (13 of 1950), shall stand repealed; and`
  line
  line `(b) the enactments specified in the Thirteenth Schedule shall cease to have effect within Delhi.`
  line
  line `(2) Notwithstanding the provisions of sub-section (1) of this section or of clause (a) of sub-section (2)`
  line `of section 286,--`
  line
  line `(a) any appointment, notification, order, scheme, rule, form, notice or bye-law made or issued,`
  line `and any licence or permission granted under any of the Acts or enactments referred to in`
  line `sub-section (1) of this section or under the Act referred to in clause (a) of sub-section (2) of section`
  line `286 and in force immediately before the establishment of ^1[^2[the Corporation]], shall, in so far as it is not`
  line `inconsistent with the provisions of this Act, continue in force and be deemed to have been made,`
  line `issued or granted under the provisions of this Act, unless and until it is superseded by any`
  line `appointment, notification, order, scheme, rule, form, notice or bye-law made or issued or any licence`
  line `or permission granted under the said provisions;`
  line
  line `(b) all debts, obligations and liabilities incurred, all contracts entered into and all matters and`
  line `things engaged to be done by, with or for any of the bodies or local authorities specified in the Second`
  line `Scheduled before such establishment shall be deemed to have been incurred, entered into or engaged`
  line `to be done by, with or for ^1[^2[the Corporation]] or the municipal authority concerned;`
  line
  line `(c) all budget estimates, assessments, valuations, measurements or divisions made by any of the`
  line `aforesaid bodies or local authorities shall in so far as they are not inconsistent with the provisions of`
  line `this Act, continue in force and be deemed to have been made under the provisions of this Act unless`
  line `and until they are superseded by any budget estimate, assessment, valuation, measurement or division`
  line `made by ^1[^2[the Corporation]] or the municipal authority concerned under the said provisions;`
  line
  line `(d) all properties, movable and immovable and all interests of whatsoever nature and kind therein,`
  line `vested in any of the aforesaid bodies and local authorities immediately before such establishment shall, with all rights of whatsoever description, used, enjoyed or possessed by any such body or`
  line `authority, vest in ^1[^2[the Corporation]];`
  line
  line `(e) all rates, taxes, fees, rents and other sums of money due to any of the aforesaid bodies or local`
  line `authorities immediately before such establishment shall be deemed to be due to ^1[^2[the Corporation]];`
  line
  line `(f) all rates, taxes, fees, rents, fares and other charges shall, until and unless they are varied by ^1[^2[the`
  line `Corporation]] continue to be levied at the same rate at which they were being levied by the aforesaid`
  line `bodies or local authorities immediately before such establishment;`
  line
  line `(g) all suits, prosecutions and other legal proceedings instituted or which might have been`
  line `instituted by or against any of the aforesaid bodies or local authorities may be continued or instituted`
  line `by or against ^1[^2[the Corporation]] .`
obj_root_law_sections_516_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Subs. by Delhi Act 12 of 2011, s. 2, for “the Corporation” (w.e.f. 13-1-2012).`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by Act 10 of 2022, s. 2, for “a Corporation” (w.e.f. 22-5-2022).`
